Class Course

java.lang.Object
Entities.Course
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Course
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Represents a course registered in STARS. A Course can contain multiple Indexes. Implements the Serializable class
